altername_name: Warau Inu no Bouken: Silly Go Lucky!
name: Warauinu no Bouken GB: Silly Go Lucky!
overview: Warau Inu no Bouken GB: Silly Go Lucky! (笑う犬の冒険GB SILLY GO LUCKY!?) is a 2001 game based on the 1999 TV series Warau Inu no Bouken: Silly Go Lucky! (lit. "The Adventures of the Laughing Dog: Silly Go Lucky!").
